this is a protocl of network control
the stand is this:

        +--------|----------------+--------+---------------------------------+--------------+                         |              |
        | cli id |   messgae id   |  code  |             option              |   message    |
        +--------+----------------+--------+---------------------------------+--------------+
        |<- 1B ->|<-     2B     ->|<- 1B ->|<-             4B              ->|<-   1000B  ->|

        cli id :client id ,every host has a unique id .             
                it is calcluatored by mac address and unix t         --        --|==|
                ime.                                                  \\  ==  // |  |
        message id:create was created by server . the server           \\//\\//  |==
                send the message id .when the client resonce         1 00  2 44
                the control message ,use the same message id         1 00  2 44
                to reply to the server.
        code : message type
                the message is defined follow:
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+
                        |  0  | 0 | responce | 1 | request |
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+
                        |  1  | 0 |          | 1 |  shell  |
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+
                        |  2  | 0 |          | 1 |         |
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+
                        |  3  | 0 |          | 1 |         |
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+
                        |  4  | 0 | succeed  | 1 |  fail   |
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+
                        |  5  | 0 |          | 1 |         |
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+
                        |  6  | 0 |          | 1 |         |
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+
                        |  7  | 0 |          | 1 |         |
                        +-----+---+----------+---+---------+


        message: message 

